{"_id":"ZeDnbuPHWSI8exIz","name":"Censer of Athena","type":"weapon","img":"Items/CenserOfZeal.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<h3>Zealous Vapours. </h3>\n<p>You create a <strong>10 foot radius</strong> cloud of incense centered on you that invigorates your allies and debilitates your foes for <strong>10 minutes</strong>. Whenever you or a friendly creature within the radius make an <strong>attack roll or saving throw</strong> they can<strong> roll a d4 and add the number</strong> rolled to the attack or saving throw. Whenever a hostile creature within the radius makes an <strong>attack roll or a saving throw the creature must roll a d4 and subtract the number rolled</strong> from the attack roll or saving throw. You must maintain concentration on this feature as though concentrating on a spell as you chant a hymn to maintain the effect for a maximum of 10 minutes. You must complete a 1 hour ritual to refresh the incense after using this feature.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Athena's Shield</h3>\n<p>When Zealous Vapours is active each creature you choose within it gains the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Cover:</strong> The creature has half cover.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Holy Resistance:</strong> The creature has resistance to acid, cold, fire, lightning, and poison damage.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Evasion:</strong> If the creature is subjected to an effect that allows it to make a Dexterity saving throw to take only half damage, the creature instead takes no damage if it succeeds on the saving throw, and only half damage if it fails.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","quantity":1,"weight":2,"price":1000,"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":10,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","tar